3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper presents a self-supervised learning approach for training the model. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with neural networks and their architecture. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating video frames.
